  "detailed_description": "The relaxing UFO hunting experience.<br>Have you ever watched the CE5 videos and though to yourself 'I wish I could expeience that'? Well now you can, whenever you want and from the comfort of your own gaming chair.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/8b33d1b47f680387ebf9a043f54211ac.poster.avif?t=1726257928\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/8b33d1b47f680387ebf9a043f54211ac.webm?t=1726257928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/8b33d1b47f680387ebf9a043f54211ac.mp4?t=1726257928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Simple gameplay that you can control with just one hand - the mouse is all you need. Your other hand could be holding a cold beer or eating nachos, while you hunt those UFO's.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/d1df9542e2bbf46eab6482804027a194.poster.avif?t=1726257928\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/d1df9542e2bbf46eab6482804027a194.webm?t=1726257928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/d1df9542e2bbf46eab6482804027a194.mp4?t=1726257928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Multiple maps to choose from. YOU set the scene and keep your eyes on the skies. Make sure to eat and drink regularly. Also you'll need coffee... and lots of it, we're gonna be out here all night! Don't worry, you'll have a fire to keep you warm.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/2e7dd0b1752424d999ec3e90722bac91.poster.avif?t=1726257928\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/2e7dd0b1752424d999ec3e90722bac91.webm?t=1726257928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151820/extras/2e7dd0b1752424d999ec3e90722bac91.mp4?t=1726257928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enjoy the peaceful nature sounds and the crackle of the fire as you gaze the stars and ponder the universe's secrets.",
